0 STANCE~
Syntax: stance <sentence containing your name>
        stance none
        stance

This command will allow you to set your short, one-line description 
which is seen by other players looking around the room you are in.  You
must include your name somewhere in the phrase. The use of obscenities,
even 'disguised' ones (like a$$ F*ck) is NOT allowed in stances.
 
Typing 'stance none' will clear your stance and default back to your
